Read Data Versions

Source: R/readDataVersions.R
readDataVersions.Rd

Read Data Versions

readDataVersions(file)

Arguments

file

string. File path.

Value

tbl_df.

Note

The data_versions.csv file is only generated for special genomes containing additional information (e.g. the built-in "hg38" build).

Examples

readDataVersions("http://bcbiobase.seq.cloud/data_versions.csv") %>%
    glimpse()
#> Parsed with column specification:
#> cols(
#>   genome = col_character(),
#>   resource = col_character(),
#>   version = col_datetime(format = "")
#> )
#> Observations: 5
#> Variables: 3
#> $ genome   <chr> "mm10", "mm10", "mm10", "mm10", "mm10"
#> $ resource <chr> "sranseq", "srnaseq", "problem_regions", "dbsnp", "transcrip…
#> $ version  <dttm> 2015-10-14, 2016-11-21, 2015-10-28, 2013-09-12, 2014-07-14
